@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Message of Chairman";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
<style>
    body { 
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
        background: #f8f9fa; 
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    
    .section-header { 
        text-align: center; 
        margin: 60px 0 30px; 
    }
    .section-header h2 { 
        font-size: 2.5rem; 
        font-weight: 700; 
        color: #2c3e50; 
    }
    .section-header p { 
        font-size: 1.1rem; 
        color: #7f8c8d; 
        max-width: 600px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
    }
    
    .chairman-content {
        max-width: 520px;
        margin: 40px auto 60px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(44,62,80,0.06);
        padding: 32px 32px 28px 32px;
    }
    .chairman-content h3 {
        color: #2563eb;
        font-size: 1.18rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        margin-top: 28px;
    }
    .chairman-content h3:first-child {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    .chairman-content p {
        font-size: 1.01rem;
        color: #222;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .chairman-signature {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #2563eb;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero-section {
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #4072b7 0%, #6a4bbf 100%); 
        color: #fff; 
        padding: 48px 20px 28px 20px; 
        text-align: center; 
        width: 100%; 
        margin-top: 80px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .hero-content {
        max-width: 900px; 
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero-title {
        font-size: 2.2rem; 
        font-weight: 700; 
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.08rem; 
        margin-bottom: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Chairman Intro Section */
    .chairman-intro {
        background: #fafbfc; 
        padding: 36px 20px 18px 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .chairman-container {
        max-width: 1100px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        display: flex; 
        align-items: flex-start; 
        gap: 40px; 
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .chairman-photo-section {
        flex: 0 0 220px; 
        text-align: center;
    }
    .chairman-photo {
        width: 270px; 
        height: 300px; 
        object-fit: cover; 
        border-radius: 6px; 
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); 
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .chairman-name {
        font-weight: 700; 
        color: #2563eb; 
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .chairman-title {
        font-size: 0.98rem; 
        color: #222;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .message-intro {
        flex: 1 1 350px; 
        min-width: 280px; 
        text-align: left;
    }
    .quote-icon {
        font-size: 2.2rem; 
        color: #4072b7; 
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .greeting {
        font-weight: 600; 
        color: #2563eb; 
        margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .intro-text {
        font-size: 1.04rem; 
        color: #222;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .chairman-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .chairman-photo-section {
            flex: none;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .chairman-photo {
            width: 220px;
            height: 250px;
        }
        .message-intro {
            flex: none;
            width: 100%;
            min-width: auto;
        }
        .quote-icon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        .chairman-content {
            margin: 30px 15px 50px 15px;
            padding: 25px 20px 20px 20px;
        }
        .chairman-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .chairman-content p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 480px) {
        .hero-section {
            padding: 40px 15px 25px 15px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .chairman-intro {
            padding: 25px 15px 15px 15px;
        }
        .chairman-photo {
            width: 180px;
            height: 200px;
        }
        .chairman-name {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .chairman-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .quote-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .chairman-content {
            margin: 25px 10px 40px 10px;
            padding: 20px 15px 15px 15px;
        }
        .chairman-content h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .chairman-content p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .chairman-signature {
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 360px) {
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .chairman-photo {
            width: 150px;
            height: 170px;
        }
        .chairman-name {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .chairman-title {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
        .quote-icon {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .chairman-content {
            margin: 20px 8px 35px 8px;
            padding: 18px 12px 12px 12px;
        }
        .chairman-content h3 {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .chairman-content p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .chairman-signature {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
    }

    /* Tablet specific adjustments */
    @@media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
        .chairman-container {
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .chairman-photo {
            width: 240px;
            height: 270px;
        }
        .chairman-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 35px auto 55px auto;
            padding: 30px 30px 25px 30px;
        }
    }

    /* Large screen adjustments */
    @@media (min-width: 1200px) {
        .chairman-content {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Message from the President</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">A personal reflection on our mission, values, and commitment to<br />serving Bangladesh's most vulnerable communities.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Chairman Intro Section -->
<section class="chairman-intro">
    <div class="chairman-container">
        <!-- Left: Chairman Photo and Name -->
        <div class="chairman-photo-section">
            <img src="@Url.Content("~/Photos/1231.jpg")" alt="Brig Gen Md Zahid Hossain, PhD (Retd)" class="chairman-photo" />
            <div class="chairman-name">Brig Gen Md Zahid Hossain, PhD (Retd)</div>
            <div class="chairman-title">Chairman &amp; President<br/>Sector 13 Welfare Society</div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right: Message Intro -->
        <div class="message-intro">
            <div class="quote-icon"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
            <div class="greeting">Assalamu Alaikum and warm greetings,</div>
            <div class="intro-text">
                When we founded Sector 13 Welfare Society in 2021, we were guided by a clear and heartfelt belief: that every individual, no matter their background or challenges, deserves respect, opportunity, and a better future. Looking back on our journey, I feel deeply honored by the trust our community has placed in us and proud of the positive change we've created together.

Our work—from supporting local families to addressing the unique needs of our community—has shown us that real progress comes not only from solving immediate problems, but from empowering people to shape their own sustainable futures.

A simple phrase continues to inspire our mission: "Together, we rise." – <span style="font-style: italic; color: #6a4bbf;">"Charity is Investment, helps you to earn Smiles"</span> – reflects our belief that every act of giving creates ripples of positive change that extend far beyond the initial gesture. When we invest in a child's education, we invest in their family's future. When we provide clean water to a village, we invest in the health and productivity of an entire community.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="chairman-content">
    <h3>Our Commitment to Excellence and Transparency</h3>
    <p>Over the past three years, we have had the privilege of directly impacting over 500,000 lives through our comprehensive programs. Each number represents a family that now has access to clean water, a child who can attend school, a patient who received life-saving medical care, or a refugee family that found hope in their darkest hour.</p>
    <p>Our work spans six major areas – Education, Food Security, Water &amp; Sanitation, Healthcare, Emergency Response, and our specialized Rohingya Response programs. Each initiative is carefully designed not just to address immediate needs, but to build long-term resilience and self-sufficiency within communities.</p>
    <h3>Partnership and Collaboration</h3>
    <p>We are deeply grateful to our partners – from international organizations like the UAE Embassy and UAE Red Crescent to local community leaders who guide our work. These partnerships have enabled us to amplify our impact and ensure that our programs are culturally sensitive and locally relevant.</p>
    <p>Our construction projects – building mosques, schools, and homes – represent more than just physical structures. They are symbols of hope, centers of community life, and foundations for future generations to build upon.</p>
    <h3>Looking Forward</h3>
    <p>As we look to the future, we are committed to expanding our reach while deepening our impact. We envision a Bangladesh where no child goes to bed hungry, where every family has access to clean water and quality healthcare, and where education is a bridge to opportunity rather than a privilege.</p>
    <p>But we cannot do this alone. Every donor, volunteer, partner, and supporter is an integral part of this mission. Your trust and generosity enable us to continue this vital work and reach more communities in need.</p>
    <p>I invite you to join us in this journey of transformation. Whether through financial support, volunteering your time, or simply spreading awareness of our work, you can be part of creating positive change in the lives of Bangladesh's most vulnerable people.</p>
    <p>Together, we can build a future where every person has the opportunity to thrive, where compassion guides our actions, and where the smiles of those we serve remind us why this work matters.</p>
    <div class="chairman-signature">
        With gratitude and determination,<br/>
        <strong>Abu Hanifa Numan</strong><br/>
        Chairman &amp; Founder, United Welfare Society
    </div>
</div> 